```
# =========================
# OLLAMA - GLOBAL IGNORE
# =========================

# -------------------------
# Model blobs (VERY LARGE)
# -------------------------
models/blobs/
models/blobs/**

# Partial downloads
models/blobs/*-partial*
models/blobs/*.tmp

# -------------------------
# Model manifests (optional)
# Keep structure, ignore content
# -------------------------
models/manifests/**
!models/manifests/
!models/manifests/registry.ollama.ai/
!models/manifests/registry.ollama.ai/library/

# -------------------------
# Local build artifacts
# -------------------------
*.log
*.cache
.cache_router/
router_metrics.json

# -------------------------
# Keys / sensitive files
# -------------------------
id_ed25519
id_ed25519.pub
*.pem
*.key

# -------------------------
# OS / editor junk
# -------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# -------------------------
# Temporary / crash files
# -------------------------
*.tmp
*.temp
*.pid
*.lock

# -------------------------
# Optional: Ignore all models completely
# (Uncomment if you NEVER want models tracked)
# -------------------------
# models/

# -------------------------
# Allow configs & modelfiles
# -------------------------
!modelfiles/
!modelfiles/**
!system-prompts/
!system-prompts/**
!config.json
!build_models.sh
```
